{"tid":1144721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美委員會質疑違香港政策法　邱騰華：話逃犯條例影響營商環境　拉得比較遠","createTime":"2019-05-08T08:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T11:43:01.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"559955db5360a97e24eeab7581d539a5a7d5cceb","tid":1144721,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T08:50:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/1153437_YHAjQ_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F1153437_YHAjQ_1200x0.png&h=9bf002ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國國會轄下美中經濟與安全審查委員會發表報告，質疑《逃犯條例》修訂違反《美港政策法》條款，或引起美國重新審視美國與香港的關係。商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華今日回應稱，修例旨在通過合法方式移交罪犯，指若把修例延伸至影響香港營商環境和其他國家的情況，「拉得比較遠」。<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華見記者時稱，港重視國際貿易關係，但指關係並非基於其他國家政府、議會、團體的意見，香港有良好經貿關係，是建基於雙方互惠互利，以及《基本法》下香港作為獨立關稅區的條文。<br />\n<br />\n對於美中經濟與安全審查委員會發表研究報告，認為《逃犯條例》修訂草案如果通過，可以擴大北京對香港的政治影響力，可能違反《美國香港政策法》。<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華稱，「如果話逃犯條例影響營商環境、以及其他國家情況，我諗係拉得比較遠。」<br />\n<br />\n邱又指，有關報告反映修例引起關注，港府有責任就修例，目標、原意、具體情況及實施情況，加以解釋和討論，故法案委員會應盡快開始審議，因此保安局局長李家超和律政政司長鄭若驊才在昨天開記者會，以法論法解釋修例，透過解釋舒緩公眾因誤解帶來的憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/美委員會質疑違香港政策法-邱騰華-話逃犯條例影響營商環境-拉得比較遠/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%83%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E9%81%95%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E6%B3%95-%E9%82%B1%E9%A8%B0%E8%8F%AF-%E8%A9%B1%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E7%87%9F%E5%95%86%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83-%E6%8B%89%E5%BE%97%E6%AF%94%E8%BC%83%E9%81%A0%2F&d=6Mci4xO0oquEcg2hov7%2FckYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=390e80b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%83%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E9%81%95%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E6%B3%95-%E9%82%B1%E9%A8%B0%E8%8F%AF-%E8%A9%B1%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E7%87%9F%E5%95%86%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83-%E6%8B%89%E5%BE%97%E6%AF%94%E8%BC%83%E9%81%A0%2F&h=384df9e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/美委員會質疑違香港政策法-邱騰華-話逃犯條例影響營商環境-拉得比較遠/</a>"},{"pid":"b75736c7cf95efd12356b41aee24b810fea72acc","tid":1144721,"uid":83228,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T08:53:06.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣書店商人人辨<br />\n攬炒"},{"pid":"a103e390a6169cf14f18b7dd15d26e213598355f","tid":1144721,"uid":217275,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T08:55:35.000Z","msg":"人地美佬up得出就咪講表面野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73736ea3cd6eec5d5f369c29e4015894993a9690","tid":1144721,"uid":137725,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T08:57:53.000Z","msg":"香港政府咪撚縮沙，嗱嗱聲通過逃犯條例<br />\n縮沙正契弟"},{"pid":"cd15daf767cc24ab7ceee3c9d50cf11a2e650fcd","tid":1144721,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T08:59:36.000Z","msg":"拉得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4fb6e5e787a14aa2243df4301f5b2a45d1f727","tid":1144721,"uid":27411,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T09:00:24.000Z","msg":"繼續講啦講多啲，中國強大喇洗乜怕美國，亮劍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e6fae03096307da83e182d1e119f039dbc05c0c","tid":1144721,"uid":42846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T09:02:48.000Z","msg":"基本法下獨立關稅區? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2951957b45a14b2788bd7aef26cf3063fb922248","tid":1144721,"uid":36321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T09:04:09.000Z","msg":"啲商家呢就用腳投票嘅"},{"pid":"7cd5e6bdceac69802bf3f9950798df99f733dd49","tid":1144721,"uid":14103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T09:11:49.000Z","msg":"係你短視啫"},{"pid":